data.description: Come see this beautiful and well-maintained single-family home located in a gated community. It has a large patio perfect for entertaining and lots of privacy. The community has a heated pool, tennis, playground, and picnic area. Close to shopping, restaurants, and major highways. The HOA fee is $700 quarterly - the HOA is just for the community. They are in charge of the maintenance of yards, common areas, roads, mailboxes, pool and trash. The property will be vacant at closing.
